00:22:31.640 --> 00:22:34.260
So we've performed
together as family

00:22:34.260 --> 00:22:39.120
in Queen Elizabeth Hall in
London and out here in Marin

00:22:39.120 --> 00:22:40.530
and places.

00:22:40.530 --> 00:22:42.850
So yeah, we work together.

00:22:42.850 --> 00:22:44.700
My older daughter--
oh, by the way,

